column10: dig_threshold_desc:Usually when the dig produced under 25 gems I would leave the planet. I used it more so after the first few rounds.
column14: dynamic_desc:If it seemed like I was getting more gems at first
column15: I'd stay but once I dropped below about 25 gems I'd leave. I also used this strategy after the first few rounds.
column18: feedback:The sound messed up a couple times like it wasn't in sync with what I was seeing. There would be digging noises when I was traveling or traveling noises after I arrived on a planet.}
